The solution uses a vector to store the generated integers and iterates through it once to generate the sequence. The time complexity is O(n) since we iterate through the vector once. The space complexity is O(1) since we only use a constant amount of space for the vector. The energy implications are low since the solution only uses a single API call for each integer generation.

